# Premount ignore list — files protected from being overwritten
# with the premount CPIO data in the ISO root directory.
#
# Lines starting with '#' are comments.
# Lines without a '/' suffix use exact (case-insensitive) name matching.
# Lines with a '/' suffix use prefix matching.
#
# Never overwrite files needed by GRUB, EFI boot, or El Torito.

BOOT.CATALOG
BOOT.CAT
GRUB.CFG
LOOPBACK.CFG
BOOTX64.EFI
BOOTIA32.EFI
GRUBX64.EFI
SHIMX64.EFI
BOOT.SDI
BCD
BOOTMGR
BOOTMGR.EFI
MEMTEST.EFI
MD5SUM*
README*
UBUNTU*
DEBIAN*
POP*
AUTORUN.INF
EFI.IMG
SHA256SUM.TXT
# Well-known directory names — never overwrite even if ISO9660 flags are wrong
CASPER
LIVE
LIVEOS
ARCH
APKS
DISTROS
POP-OS
SYSTEM
SOURCES
# Alpine marker files — scanner relies on these to detect Alpine ISOs
.ALPINE-RELEASE
.ALPINE_RELEASE
